<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is one of those series that you should read from the beginning. It could just have easily been one long book and been just as good.<br/><br/>Would you watc<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is one of those series that you should read from the beginning. It could just have easily been one long book and been just as good.<br /><br />Would you watch a Netflix series starting from a random episode? :)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
