<li class='cover' id='bookCover_41954116'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41954116-genesis"><img alt="Genesis (Wayward Pines)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1537479088l/41954116._SX98_.jpg" />
